title: GAME INVENTORY SOUNDS: PACK2
description: This audio asset pack contains a total of 208 everyday foley sounds of items such as wheel chair, rummaging, cardboard box, jewelry, ornaments, coins, keychains, zippers, boxes, bags, etc
longDescription:
AUDIO DEMO


''GAME INVENTORY SOUNDS: PACK2'' contains the following foley sound effects that are useful in everyday tasks.

Each sound type has multiple variations. We created all the sounds originally at 96kHz/24bit.

The sounds are organized into three audio specs as mentioned in the technical details.

  1. bag handling
  2. bag zipper open close type1
  3. bag zipper open close type2
  4. bag zipper open close type3
  5. carboard box handling
  6. currency bank-notes counting handling
  7. dice shaking
  8. fabric rubbing handling
  9. jewellery ornaments gold-coins handling
  10. key-chain type1
  11. key-chain type2
  12. key-chain type3
  13. key-chain type4
  14. key-chain type5
  15. key-chain type6
  16. key-chain type7
  17. rummaging small box
  18. Velcro
  19. wheel chair movement
